A small extension for Ruby that provides access to Xlib in order to perform window management functions.

Frank Hale <frankhale@gmail.com>
Started: 23 May 2005

This code is released under the GNU GPL version 3

To build the extension at a command prompt type:

ruby extconf.rb 

after it creates the makefile

make

The examples should be able to be ran in place. No need to install anything.
